1
00:00:04,128 --> 00:00:06,466
One lady got initiated,
and she said,

2
00:00:06,466 --> 00:00:10,916
“What should I do 
for my morning sādhana?”

3
00:00:10,916 --> 00:00:13,856
And I said, 
“What are you doing now?”

4
00:00:13,856 --> 00:00:16,265
She said, 
“Oh, I chant …

5
00:00:16,265 --> 00:00:19,265
My daughter and I,
we chant the Nārāyaṇ kavacha.”

6
00:00:19,265 --> 00:00:23,365
[Don’t Miss the Point]

7
00:00:24,088 --> 00:00:25,988
I said,
“Why did you do that?”
 

8
00:00:25,988 --> 00:00:29,240
She said, “Well, we’ve read in the book.“
It says, “It’s so auspicious,

9
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:33,357
and it should be done,
and everyone should …”

10
00:00:34,107 --> 00:00:36,886
But interestingly, 
even in Prabhupād’s lifetime

11
00:00:36,886 --> 00:00:39,351
one of his disciples, 
leading disciples,

12
00:00:39,351 --> 00:00:42,351
reported to him
that he was doing that.

13
00:00:42,351 --> 00:00:45,172
And Prabhupad said,
“Why are you doing this?”

14
00:00:45,172 --> 00:00:47,454
He said, 
“It’s you wrote in your book,
 

15
00:00:47,454 --> 00:00:49,644
one should do this
and how important it is,
 

16
00:00:49,644 --> 00:00:52,219
and you’ll get this,
and you …”

17
00:00:52,219 --> 00:00:55,773
So, you read in a purport
something that to him

18
00:00:55,773 --> 00:00:59,306
it seemed like Prabhupād 
was giving a resounding,

19
00:00:59,306 --> 00:01:03,984
wholesale, full recommendation 
to do this.

20
00:01:03,984 --> 00:01:06,163
But when 
he talked to him personally,

21
00:01:06,163 --> 00:01:11,209
he told, “I never told you to do that.
I’m not asking you to do that.”

22
00:01:11,209 --> 00:01:13,801
But he said, 
“Well, in the book …”

23
00:01:13,801 --> 00:01:17,710
That’s another thing. 
There are so many things.

24
00:01:17,710 --> 00:01:19,800
They’ll say,
“One who hears this,

25
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:22,777
one who does that, 
one should …
 

26
00:01:22,777 --> 00:01:25,347
is advised 
to do this.”

27
00:01:25,347 --> 00:01:27,775
But that’s why 
we have guru—
 

28
00:01:27,775 --> 00:01:30,775
sādhu, sāstra, 
guru, Vaiṣṇav.

29
00:01:30,775 --> 00:01:34,605
We have the scriptures
and then the living scriptures.

